high_descs: Turn to your left then slight forward then turn right then head to the sink
Pick up the mug on the sink
Turn to your left and head to the microwave
Put the mug in then wait few second get it out then close the microwave
Turn to your right, face the coffee maker
put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mug on the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn around and when you get to the door on the left, turn right and head to the sink.
Pick up the mug closest to the faucet from the sink.
Carry the mug to the microwave on your left.
Open the microwave, place the mug inside, turn it on, and then remove once heated.
Turn and carry the mug to the coffee maker on your right, which is just left of the sink.
Place the mug on the base of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated mug on the base of the coffee maker.

high_descs: move to the sink to the left of the stove
pick up a mug from the sink
move to the microwave to the left
heat the mug in the microwave
move to the coffee maker to the left of the sink
put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee maker.
